n<\/strong>: We may collect personal information, such as your name, email address, phone number, and company details when you contact us, fill out forms, or subscribe to our updates.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Usage Data<\/strong>: Our website collects usage information, including IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time spent on each page, to enhance your browsing experience and optimize our services.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. How We Use Your Information<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Service Provision<\/strong>: We use your personal information to communicate with you, respond to inquiries, and provide the services you request.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Improvement of Website and Services<\/strong>: Usage data helps us analyze and enhance our website\u2019s functionality, ensuring a better user experience.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Marketing and Updates<\/strong>: With your consent, we may use your contact details to send occasional newsletters, service updates, or marketing materials. You may opt-out at any time by contacting us.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Information Sharing and Disclosure<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Third-Party Service Providers<\/strong>: We may share information with trusted third-party vendors who assist us with website hosting, data analysis, payment processing, and customer support. These providers are obligated to protect your data and only use it for their specific purposes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Legal Compliance<\/strong>: We may disclose your information when required to comply with legal obligations, protect our rights, or ensure safety for our clients and team.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Data Security<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to provide a better user experience, such as remembering your preferences. You can control cookies through your browser settings; however, this may limit some website features.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Your Rights<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You have the right to access, update, correct, or delete the personal information we hold about you. To make a request, please contact us at <strong><a>info@gmglobalsolutions.org<\/a><\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Third-Party Links<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our website may contain links to external sites that are not operated by us. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these websites and encourage you to review their privacy policies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. Any changes will be posted on this page, with an updated \u201cEffective Date.\u201d We encourage you to review this policy from time to time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Contact Us<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy, please reach out to us:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Email<\/strong>: <a>info@gmglobalsolutions.org<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>Thank you for trusting Staunch with your information. We are dedicated to ensuring a secure and transparent experience with us.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Effective Date: November 7, 2024 Staunch (\u201cwe,\u201d \u201cus,\u201d or \u2